reviewText: Hi. A great concert from Umphrey'McGee in Red Rocks. Perfect sound and image. Great job. Thank you. Abilio

I'm a big fan of UM and this latest addition to my UM collection didn't fail me. There are better set lists by UM at Red Rocks (they've performed there numerous times) and my favorite was from June 2013. Nevertheless, I'm not disappointed at all. UM ROCKS!!
the music is great and the light show was fantastic but I was disappointed at the sound was not true hd or master audio it wasn't even 5.1
